s_{x\hat{r}}=\sum{(x_i-\bar{x})(r_i - \bar{r}}) = \sum{(x_i-\bar{x})(y_i-\alpha -\beta x_i- \bar{r})}
s_{x\hat{r}}= \sum{(x_i-\bar{x})(y_i-\alpha -\beta x_i)} - \bar{r}\sum{(x_i-\bar{x})}
s_{x\hat{r}}=\sum{(x_i-\bar{x})(y_i-\alpha -\beta x_i)}
